<!-- Game Description Table -->

<table class="tablestyle" id="table14" cellspacing="4" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td class="sectional">

<!-- Game Description Header -->
		
		<table class="headertable" id="table15" cellspacing="2" cellpadding="2">
			<tr>
				<td class="headercell">
				<img border="0" src="../../../images/headers/gamedes.jpg" width="240" height="33"></td>
			</tr>
		</table>

<!-- Game Description Sectional -->

<table border="0" width="100%" id="table16" cellpadding="0">
	<tr>
		<td style="font-family: Trebuchet MS; font-size: 8pt; color: #FFFFFF; font-weight: bold; text-align: left; background-color: #333333; border-left: 2px solid #000000; border-right: 2px solid #FFFFFF; border-top: 2px solid #000000; border-bottom: 2px solid #FFFFFF">
			<br>After a horrible death by burning, Al Simmons finds himself in the eighth sphere of Hell; making deals with a head honcho named Malebolgia. Trading his freedom for one last glimpse of his wife, Simmons is called to lead Hell's army in the final battle of Armageddon as Spawn. Players will guide Spawn through 15 worlds of battle against a variety of monsters in an effort to face and destroy Malebolgia, ultimately gaining eternal freedom.
                  <br><br>Features:
                  <br>* Take out your enemies with magic, cape, and chain attacks as you explore 15 different worlds
                  <br>* Work your way back to Hell in order to face and destroy Malebolgia and gain your freedom
                  <br>* Explore each level to uncover secrets , magic, and keys that can help you through your adventure
                  <br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>Manufacturer's description:</u><br>
                  <br>Todd McFarlane's Dark Comic Hero Is Unleashed. Only A Fight In Hell Will Save His Soul!
                  <br><br>When Spawn's hell-born rage explodes, can anything survive?
                  <br><br>* Featuring America's #1 comic book characters including Overtkill, Tiffany, Vandalizer, Vaporizer, Violator, and the hellion Malebolgia.
                  <br>* Engage in blood gushing hand-to-hand slaughter and rip the limbs from your opponents.
                  <br>* Execute magic, cape and chain-based attacks.
                  <br>* Over 15 enormous and deadly 3D worlds.
                  <br>* Uncover secrets, magic and keys for a challenging adventure game experience.
                  <br><br>Also released in a limited edition chromium cover.
                  <br><br>&nbsp;&nbsp;<u>Features:</u><br>
			<ul><li>Third person perspective.</li>
			<li>3D graphics</li>
			<li>Cartoon graphics</li>
			<li>Demons, Fantasy & Comic themes.</li></ul>
</td>

	</tr>
	</table>
	       	</td>
     </tr>
</table>  

