		    <br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">MISC CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; All Inventory -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Pause the game, hold L2 + R2 and press X, Square, Circle, Triangle, Square, Circle</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp; All Power Ups (press L2 + R2 during play to restore energy levels) -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Pause the game, hold L2 + R2 and press Triangle, Circle, Square, X, Triangle, X</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp; Invisibility -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Pause the game, hold L1 + R1 and press Square, Square, Circle, Circle, Triangle, X</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp; Invulnerability -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Pause the game, hold L1 + R1 and press Triangle, Triangle, X, X, Square, Circle</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp; Level Skip -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Hold L1, R1, L2 and press Triangle, X, Square, Circle, Circle, Circle</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp; Refill Health -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Pause the game, hold L1 + R1 and press X, Circle, Triangle, Square, X, Circle</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp; Refill Magic -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00">Pause the game, hold L1 + R1 and press Triangle, Circle, X, Square, Triangle, Circle</font>&nbsp;<br>
          		<br><u><i><font color="#FFFF00">ACTION REPLAY CODES:</font></i></u><br>
			&nbsp; Infinite Hell Gauntlet -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>8007F09A 0500</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp;  Infinite Energy -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>8007F050 0800</font>&nbsp;
				  <br>&nbsp;  Infinite Magic Level -
                  &nbsp; <font color="#00FF00"><br>8007F052 270F</font>&nbsp;<br><br>
	 </tr>
